--><div class="t075"><div class="t-container"><div class="t-col t-col_4 t-align_left"><div class="t075__wrapperleft t075__textclass1"><div class="t075__title t-name" style="" field="title">Fast load time—images are stored on CDN</div><div class="t-text" style="" field="descr">Images are stored on a geographically distributed network (CDN) that reduces load times thanks to a number of proxy servers deployed in multiple locations.</div></div></div><div class="t-col t-col_4 t-align_left"><div class="t075__wrapperleft t075__textclass1"><div class="t075__title t-name" style="" field="title2">Connecting HTTPS</div><div class="t-text" style="" field="descr2">Install a free LetsEncrypt certificate in your Site settings, or download your SSL certificate.</div></div></div><div class="t-col t-col_4 t-align_left"><div class="t075__wrapperleft t075__textclass1"><div class="t075__title t-name" style="" field="title3">Protection from DDoS Attacks</div><div class="t-text" style="" field="descr3">We use dedicated high-quality technical equipment to protect your website from intruders.</div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="rec55688471" class="r t-rec t-rec_pt_0 t-rec_pb_0" style="padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:0px;background-color:#f5f5f5; " data-animationappear="off" data-record-type="86" data-bg-color="#f5f5f5"><!-- T075 --><div class="t075"><div class="t-container"><div class="t-col t-col_4 t-align_left"><div class="t075__wrapperleft t075__textclass1"><div class="t075__title t-name" style="" field="title">301 redirect</div><div class="t-text" style="" field="descr">Enable 301 redirect to improve SEO when you change your website URL.</div></div></div><div class="t-col t-col_4 t-align_left"><div class="t075__wrapperleft t075__textclass1"><div class="t075__title t-name" style="" field="title2">Image optimization</div><div class="t-text" style="" field="descr2">All websites created on Tilda are Lazy Load-enabled by default. This allows content to download very quickly even on mobile devices.</div></div></div><div class="t-col t-col_4 t-align_left"><div class="t075__wrapperleft t075__textclass1"><div class="t075__title t-name" style="" field="title3">Adaptive Image Loading</div><div class="t-text" style="" field="descr3">The total size of a website is reduced 3-7 times thanks to this technology. The script scales images to the size of the layout container and converts them to a next-gen format—WebP. This optimization significantly speeds up all Tilda websites.</div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="rec55688815" class="r t-rec t-rec_pt_150 t-rec_pb_90" style="padding-top:150px;padding-bottom:90px;background-color:#f5f5f5; " data-animationappear="off" data-record-type="33" data-bg-color="#f5f5f5"><!-- T017 --><div class="t017"><div class="t-container t-align_center"><div class="t-col t-col_10 t-prefix_1"> <div class="t017__title t-title t-title_xxs" field="title"><div style="font-size:40px;" data-customstyle="yes">Animation</div></div> </div></div></div></div><div id="rec55688816" class="r t-rec t-rec_pt_0 t-rec_pb_0" style="padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:0px;background-color:#f5f5f5; " data-animationappear="off" data-record-type="86" data-bg-color="#f5f5f5"><!-- T075 --><div class="t075"><div class="t-container"><div class="t-col t-col_4 t-align_left"><div class="t075__wrapperleft t075__textclass1"><div class="t075__title t-name" style="" field="title"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Basic animation in ready-to-use blocks</span></div><div class="t-text" style="" field="descr"><span style="font-weight: 300;">Easily implement ready-made effects for text blocks, pictures, forms, or buttons.</span></div></div></div><div class="t-col t-col_4 t-align_left"><div class="t075__wrapperleft t075__textclass1"><div class="t075__title t-name" style="" field="title2"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Advanced animation in Zero Block</span></div><div class="t-text" style="" field="descr2">Fade in &amp; fade out animation for any element, parallax effect, fixed positioning on scroll, and a variety of trigger types. </div></div></div><div class="t-col t-col_4 t-align_left"><div class="t075__wrapperleft t075__textclass1"><div class="t075__title t-name" style="" field="title3"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Step-by-step animation</span><br /><span style="font-weight: 400;"><span class="ql-cursor">﻿</span></span></div><div class="t-text" style="" field="descr3">Motion sequences allow you to modify various attributes of an element: position, duration, scale, opacity, rotation, and more. </div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="rec9581891" class="r t-rec t-rec_pt_150 t-rec_pb_90" style="padding-top:150px;padding-bottom:90px;background-color:#f5f5f5; " data-animationappear="off" data-record-type="33" data-bg-color="#f5f5f5"><!-- T017 --><div class="t017"><div class="t-container t-align_center"><div class="t-col t-col_10 t-prefix_1"> <div class="t017__title t-title t-title_xxs" field="title"><div style="font-size: 40px;" data-customstyle="yes">Analytics</div></div> </div></div></div></div><div id="rec55690054" class="r t-rec t-rec_pt_0 t-rec_pb_60" style="padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:60px;background-color:#f5f5f5; " data-animationappear="off" data-record-type="86" data-bg-color="#f5f5f5"><!-- T075 --><div class="t075"><div class="t-container"><div class="t-col t-col_4 t-align_left"><div class="t075__wrapperleft t075__textclass1"><div class="t075__title t-name" style="" field="title"><span style="font-weight: 400;">On-site statistics service</span></div><div class="t-text" style="" field="descr">Track sessions, sources and popular pages in our ready-to-use internal statistics service. Track UTM tags, events and measure conversion, too.</div></div></div><div class="t-col t-col_4 t-align_left"><div class="t075__wrapperleft t075__textclass1"><div class="t075__title t-name" style="" field="title2"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Google Аnalytics and Google Tag Manager</span><br /></div><div class="t-text" style="" field="